### 异常路径：管理员不能撤销普通员工创建的个人自用项目节点完成状态，预期 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableEmployeeReopenNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableEmployeeReopenNodeId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：当前项目仍为已完成，必须先撤销项目完成，预期 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableCompletedProjectIdForNodeReopen}}/nodes/{{repeatableCompletedProjectNodeIdForReopen}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

