}

### 异常路径：普通员工撤销非本人负责项目节点完成状态，预期 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReopenNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminReopenNodeId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：当前不是已完成状态，不能撤销完成，预期 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableNotCompletedNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableNotCompletedNodeId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：project_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{invalidProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminReopenNodeId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：node_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReopenNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{invalidNodeId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON 对象，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReopenNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminReopenNodeId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

[]

### 异常路径：项目不存在，预期 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{missingProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminReopenNodeId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：阶段节点不存在，预期 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReopenNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{missingNodeId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}
